nodes.text: Al'art was a General of the Royal Naboo Security Forces, a starfighter ace, and a so-called Royal Forces Vindicator. Sometime following the Battle of Yavin in 0 BBY, Al'art was seen on patrol in a Z-95 Headhunter in the Naboo system.

Al'art was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies: Jump to Lightspeed, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
